Help us to lie down, /SCD/XXEAR /XXO/XXNE/XX, our God, in peace, and let us
rise again, our sovereign, to life. Spread over us the shelter of
your peace. Decree for us a worthy daily lot, and redeem us for
the sake of your great name, and enfold us in the wings of your
protection, for you are our redeeming guardian. Truly, a
sovereign, gracious, and compassionate God are you. Guard our
going forth each day for life and peace, now and always. Spread
over us the shelter of your peace./PR
/PR
